<topic id='attribute_lodging_start_time.description'>
  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>Attribute: LODGING START TIME - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>

  <p>
The time when medical staff with 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_right_of_admission">RIGHTS OF ADMISSION</xref>
 to 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_hospital_bed">Hospital Beds</xref>
 take clinical responsibility for a 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>
, but the 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>
 has to remain waiting in the nursing care of an 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_accident_and_emergency_department">Accident and Emergency Department</xref>
 until they can be transferred to a 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_ward">WARD</xref>
. This starts a period of time as a 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_lodged_patient">LODGED PATIENT</xref>
.  </p>

